strings: <voice_0x01001C85><se_high>media princess: I still remember the first time I entered the palace. Us for 8 years. It's incredible that we've known each other for 10 years!
<voice_0x01001C86><se_high>media princess: You are an orphan who lives on the earth. Even the palace guards played a part!
<voice_0x01001C87><se_high>media princess: I have a secret <hero>. I recommend your parents for this work.
<voice_0x01001C88><se_high>media princess: It's a way to get closer to you and me, so we can spend more time together. After all, you deserve it <hero>!
<voice_0x01001C89><se_high>media princess: To the brave defenders of my castle. I hope that someone will come for my next birthday. I knew you could!
